	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="regest1">
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salus et pax Christi.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nec iam michi ullum scribendi argumentum est, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Bullingere</persName> charissime, hoc uno, quod <persName ref="p7201" cert="high">Iacobus</persName><note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1">Gemeint ist zweifellos <persName ref="p7201" cert="high">Jakob Zorn</persName>; vgl. unten <ref target="file11290">Nr. 1247</ref>.</note> ille, qui nuper apud te miseriam suam detexit, anxie rogavit, ut commendaretur a me tibi.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Est autem bonus certe vir, dignus, cui adsis, si qua ratione potes.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Persequuntur illum quidam furiosi ad internitiem usque.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Invasit eum hisce diebus nebulo quidam nemini notus et prostratum conatus est vulnerare, sed defendit eum pileus insigniter lęsus, ut intelligat se non posse sine vitae discrimine diutius hic hęrere<note xml:id="fnb" type="footnote" n="b"><hi>nach</hi> haerere <hi>gestrichenes</hi> posse.</note>, atque ea est publica <placeName type="citizen_name" cert="high" ref="l774">Turgoye</placeName> iustitia, scilicet ut bonus vir non sit tutus.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominus respitiat aliquando suos.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="manual">Amen.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nosti forte <persName ref="p5565" cert="high">Capitonem</persName> brevi profecturum <placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Bernam</placeName><note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2">Das Gerücht, <persName ref="p5565" cert="high">Capito</persName> wolle <placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Bern</placeName> besuchen, bewahrheitete sich nicht; vgl. unten <ref target="file11267">Nr. 1224</ref>, 87-89.</note>; causam vero ignoro.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale cum <persName ref="p8127" cert="high">Pellicano</persName> et bonis omnibus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ex <placeName ref="l457" cert="high">Constantia</placeName>, 7. ianuarii 1539.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus <persName ref="p4079" cert="high">Io. Zvick</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse auf der Rückseite:]</note>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Domino <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Hainricho Bullingero</persName>, ecclesiae <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name">Tigurinę</placeName> antistiti, observando meo in Christo fratri.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Zürch.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
